# Depth / 3D Sensing Pipeline Integration Guide

## Overview

The Depth / 3D Sensing Pipeline provides a unified interface for time-of-flight
(ToF) sensors, structured-light projectors, and stereo camera pairs. Raw depth
data flows through calibration, rectification, and disparity stages into dense
point clouds that can be registered, fused, and fed into SLAM back-ends.

