## ICP Registration

Iterative Closest Point (ICP) and Normal Distributions Transform (NDT) are
available for aligning consecutive point clouds.

```python
from backend.depth_sensing import register_clouds, RegistrationConfig

reg_cfg = RegistrationConfig(
    method="icp",
    max_iterations={{ registration.max_iterations }},
    tolerance={{ registration.tolerance }},
)
transform = register_clouds(source_cloud, target_cloud, reg_cfg)
aligned = source_cloud.transform(transform)
```

