## SLAM Integration

The pipeline exposes hooks for visual and LiDAR SLAM systems. A SLAM back-end
receives registered point clouds and odometry and maintains a global map.

```python
from backend.depth_sensing import SLAMHook

slam = SLAMHook(backend="{{ slam.default_backend }}")
slam.initialize(intrinsics, initial_pose)
for cloud, odom in stream:
    slam.update(cloud, odom)
global_map = slam.get_map()
```

