## Calibration Guide

### Intrinsic Calibration

Estimate focal length, principal point, and distortion coefficients from a
checkerboard pattern.

```python
from backend.depth_sensing import calibrate_intrinsics

intrinsics = calibrate_intrinsics(
    images=checkerboard_images,
    board_size=({{ calibration.board_cols }}, {{ calibration.board_rows }}),
    square_size_mm={{ calibration.square_size_mm }},
)
```

### Stereo Calibration

Compute the extrinsic relationship between a stereo camera pair.

```python
from backend.depth_sensing import calibrate_stereo

stereo_calib = calibrate_stereo(
    left_images=left_checkerboard,
    right_images=right_checkerboard,
    board_size=({{ calibration.board_cols }}, {{ calibration.board_rows }}),
    square_size_mm={{ calibration.square_size_mm }},
)
```

### ToF Phase Calibration

Correct phase-offset and multi-path errors for ToF sensors.

```python
from backend.depth_sensing import calibrate_tof_phase

phase_calib = calibrate_tof_phase(
    sensor=sensor,
    reference_distances_mm={{ calibration.tof_reference_distances }},
    num_captures={{ calibration.tof_num_captures }},
)
sensor.apply_calibration(phase_calib)
```

## REST API

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/depth/sensors` | List supported depth sensors |
| GET | `/api/depth/algorithms` | List disparity / registration algorithms |
| POST | `/api/depth/capture` | Capture a depth frame |
| POST | `/api/depth/stereo/rectify` | Rectify a stereo image pair |
| POST | `/api/depth/stereo/disparity` | Compute disparity map |
| POST | `/api/depth/point-cloud` | Generate point cloud from depth |
| POST | `/api/depth/register` | Register two point clouds (ICP/NDT) |
| POST | `/api/depth/calibrate/intrinsic` | Run intrinsic calibration |
| POST | `/api/depth/calibrate/stereo` | Run stereo calibration |
| POST | `/api/depth/calibrate/tof-phase` | Run ToF phase calibration |
| POST | `/api/depth/slam/update` | Push frame into SLAM pipeline |
| GET | `/api/depth/slam/map` | Retrieve current SLAM map |
